Setup Fastly:

1)
Domain: [name].global.ssl.fastly.net
Address: IP Address for Origin server
Verify certificate : No
=> Next

2)
- Contact SATA : add domain alias

3) Config on manage.fastly.com
- Disable GZIP on Fastly
- Get Service ID :
Go to Configure tab (on top menu) : Click Show Service ID
- Get Token :
Go to Account page: Personal API tokens : Create new token

4) Go to Magento Admin
- Replace domain to [name].global.ssl.fastly.net
- Fill all info
- use features "Verify SSL"
- use the Fastly Module to upload VCL


See detail at: http://www.forixkb.com/knowledge-base/forix-speed-package/
